HEADWORD: columnist
<hw>col"um*nist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a journalist who
writes or edits a regularly scheduled column{8} in a periodical, usually
in editorial style; a type of <isa>editorialist</isa>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>RP</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>fifth columnist</b></col> <cd>see <er>fifth
columnist</er> in the vocabulary.</cd></cs></p>

